{"tid":2491173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美警擊斃13歲男孩畫面曝！中槍前已舉高雙手投降","createTime":"2021-04-16T06:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T06:53:38.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf2427136f4c50c4b95c58fdd602f06fd71d2ba","tid":2491173,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:18:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TkB4_nIfODo?t=91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTkB4_nIfODo%3Ft%3D91&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLY%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=ff9079dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TkB4_nIfODo?t=91</a><br />\n<br />\n美國芝加哥警方上月29日在暗黑的小巷中擊斃一名墨西哥裔13歲少年托萊多（Adam Toled<br />\no），指他持有槍械。但根據警方近日公開的秘錄器畫面，托萊多被警員叫喊之後就舉起<br />\n雙手轉身，且不見他手持武器，但警員最終仍開槍，引發大批民眾示威抗議。<br />\n <br />\n根據秘錄器畫面，當另名21歲嫌犯被逮捕時，一名員警沿著小巷追著托萊多跑並大喊：「<br />\n警察！停下！現在立刻停下來！雙手舉高！讓我看見你的雙手！」而當托萊多舉起雙手轉<br />\n身時，並沒有看到手持槍枝，但該警員高喊「放下槍」後就朝托萊多開槍，且擊中他的胸<br />\n部，最終死亡。該警員從下了警車開始追捕到開槍，過程僅花19秒。<br />\n <br />\n芝加哥市長萊特富特（Lori Lightfoot）形容，片段令人難以直視，尤其是片尾的部分，<br />\n並說「我們讓亞當（死者）失望了」，指沒有證據顯示死者當時向警員開槍，並呼籲示威<br />\n者保持冷靜。<br />\n <br />\n警方表示，開槍的是34歲白人警員斯蒂爾曼（Eric Stillman），2015年8月就加入警隊。<br />\n斯蒂爾曼尚未被正式指控犯下錯誤，在調查結果出爐前，他將負責行政事務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/2bAK9v\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2F2bAK9v&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLY%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=88dc502f\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/2bAK9v</a>"},{"pid":"e8cdaeac6e698e1e8df3126425e135331e47ed59","tid":2491173,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:18:58.000Z","msg":"又係死黑9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8da4eccfc5c6092249a4051989559a66c31eaab","tid":2491173,"uid":23061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:44:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ext.fmkorea.com/files/attach/new/20180628/486616/1023120581/1127316126/210e0360679849afd91957839430a443.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fext.fmkorea.com%2Ffiles%2Fattach%2Fnew%2F20180628%2F486616%2F1023120581%2F1127316126%2F210e0360679849afd91957839430a443.jpg&h=7face427&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4102688cc75bbf790d617c07a6add6db686cf70","tid":2491173,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:46:40.000Z","msg":"ACAB 全世界警察大部分都心理變態"},{"pid":"6a4542f141ab83acb1d37aa787182eb014137516","tid":2491173,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8cdaeac6e698e1e8df3126425e135331e47ed59","tid":2491173,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:18:58.000Z","msg":"又係死黑9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:48:00.000Z","msg":"墨西哥喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48359fef27a132814fc692816bdb8ca1a40d3bd4","tid":2491173,"uid":80178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebf2427136f4c50c4b95c58fdd602f06fd71d2ba","tid":2491173,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:18:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TkB4_nIfODo?t=91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTkB4_nIfODo%3Ft%3D91&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLY%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=ff9079dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TkB4_nIfODo?t=91</a><br />\n<br />\n美國芝加哥警方上月29日在暗黑的小巷中擊斃一名墨西哥裔13歲少年托萊多（Adam Toled<br />\no），指他持有槍械。但根據警方近日公開的秘錄器畫面，托萊多被警員叫喊之後就舉起<br />\n雙手轉身，且不見他手持武器，但警員最終仍開槍，引發大批民眾示威抗議。<br />\n <br />\n根據秘錄器畫面，當另名21歲嫌犯被逮捕時，一名員警沿著小巷追著托萊多跑並大喊：「<br />\n警察！停下！現在立刻停下來！雙手舉高！讓我看見你的雙手！」而當托萊多舉起雙手轉<br />\n身時，並沒有看到手持槍枝，但該警員高喊「放下槍」後就朝托萊多開槍，且擊中他的胸<br /